{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十四回 恐怖陷阱\n\n常笑逼问血奴血鹦鹉的秘密，血奴拒绝透露并与常笑发生冲突。李大娘利用血奴牵制常笑，趁机逃入照壁后的暗门。常笑、王风、血奴三人追入地下暗道，发现石门上刻有西域文字\"宝库\"二字。常笑凭借父亲传授的西域文字知识辨认出文字含义。三人进入宝库地道后遭遇机关陷阱——顶壁暗藏千百支尖枪，但机关失灵未触发。他们继续深入，听到石门后传来李大娘的惨叫，三人合力推开石门，进入一个碧绿色火焰笼罩的地下石室，发现珍贵的箱子和神秘的火焰。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我将血鹦鹉的秘密告诉这位常大人，你说好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "是你不肯答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "即使你不肯答应，只要你的母亲答应，你好像也没有办法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "她若是胆敢跟你说出那个秘密，我们与她之间的约定就完了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "完了又如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我们便可以放开手，用我们所喜欢的方法处理这件事情。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "反正已不再成为秘密，又还有什么顾虑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你们一直在顾虑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "如果她对我说出了那个秘密，你们准备如何对付她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "她是说给我知道，我知道那个秘密之后，你们是不是连我也要一起解决？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你们有这个本领？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "就算我们没有这种本领，让你逃出这个平安镇，将她留下来，相信总可以。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "拼不了常笑，难不成也拼不了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你口中的所谓'我们'，到底包括些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你们与李大娘之间究竟有什么约定？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "看来我是很难从你那里问出什么了？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你这边大概还不成问题。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我若落在他的手中，那个秘密十九保不住，秘密一揭露，就不止约定，一切都完了，他即使不杀我，活下去也是没有意思。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我知道你是怎样的一个人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你那个敢死保镖无疑一定会保护你的生命安全，却未必会替你杀掉他，只凭你一个人，就算还有其他的血奴及时赶到，能否将他留下来仍是一个问题。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "一旦被他带着秘密走脱，你仍活下去也都没有意思的了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "到时就不止魔王，血鹦鹉与那些奴才连带那十万神魔只怕也脱不了关系？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你到底要我怎样？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "只要有人替我将常笑截下片刻，我便有机会脱身……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里走！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你想知道血鹦鹉的秘密，最好就给我拉住她。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那照壁画着的地方是不是奇浓嘉嘉普？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "除了奇浓嘉嘉普，是不是还有第二个这样的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "这道门通往什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "真的不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你说现在怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "追进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你先走还是我先走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "当然是你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你害怕里头暗藏埋伏？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你害怕还是我害怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你随时都已准备与人拼命，命你都可以不要，还有什么可以使你害怕的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "说我害怕的可又是你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你不要命我却还要命，自然得请你在前开路，我随后进入。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我虽然不要命，可没有准备给你拼命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你不是很想知道，血鹦鹉的秘密？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我很想，不过你比我还想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你这个人虽然不怕死，却是死也不肯吃亏。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "这要看的是为了什么人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "好像我这种人自然就不在考虑之例。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那边还有一张几子，你替我拿来行不行。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你看得懂门上的花纹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那并不是什么花纹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "不是花纹是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "是一种文字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我看就完全不像。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你喜欢不喜欢看佛经？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "不喜欢，我甚至对和尚都没有好感。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你家中可有人做过官，出使过西域？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "一个都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这就难怪你没有看过这种文字，不懂这种文字的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "这是西域的文字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "错不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "西域的文字你也看得懂？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你似乎忘记了，我本来是什么人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我同样不喜欢和尚，所以也没有看过那边传来的佛经。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你只是出使过西域？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "还没有这种经验。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我那个父亲却是经验丰富，他也很为我设想，所以自小教我那种文字，好让我长大之后继承他的职位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你好像并不是一个听话的儿子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我现在的职位不是更好？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "他那是白费心机的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我本也以为学非所用，浪费了大好的一段日子，但现在看来，倒不是全无用处……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "石门上的文字到底是什么意思。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "也没有多大意思，那其实只不过两个字。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "哪两个字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "宝库！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "据我所知但凡是宝库，门口如果没有严密的守护，一定暗藏厉害的机关，以狙杀觊觎宝库的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "是这样的话，早已发动了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这丈许不到的地方本就是装置机关最适当的地方。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "本就是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你什么时候发觉这个机关？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "在你说出'宝库'两字的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那个时候顶壁上面的几个洞是否已经打开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "已经打开了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我看我们一踏上地道，那个机关便已开始发动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我们踏上这地道之时，顶壁上却没有洞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这机关布置显然出自高手，是以你我耳目虽灵敏事先竞也毫无感觉，若是机关一发动，洞口一打开，尖枪便落下，你我现在就不死也已重伤。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 641
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我一眼瞥见，赶紧退后之时实在已经太迟了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "洞口一打开尖枪其实就应该落下，莫非这机关出了什么毛病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我看就是了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那石门也许亦是由机关控制，如果机关真的失灵，要将它打开，不是很麻烦就一定很容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 653
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是李大娘！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "莫非她遇上了什么危险？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "左右推动着看！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    }
  ],
